articles.title: South Africa snake on plane: Deadly cobra in cockpit forces emergency landing - BBC
articles.description: "I felt this cool sensation crawling up my shirt" before spotting the snake, the pilot tells the BBC.
articles.content:
It felt like just another flight for South African pilot Rudolph Erasmus, until he noticed an extra passenger on his plane at 11,000ft in the air.
